{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9930bfac15","title":"对两报一刊社论稿《在胜利的大道上奋勇前进》的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2a9fdab28e","index":0,"year":1968,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"9930bfac15"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/50-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji50":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f107e71b7e","type":"title","text":"对两报一刊社论稿《在胜利的大道上奋勇前进》“的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"9930bfac15"},{"id":"1a0b926b08","type":"paragraph","text":"照发。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"9930bfac15"},{"id":"c45b422cb6","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]这篇社论稿是《人民日报》、《红旗》杂志、《解放军报》为庆祝中华人民共和国成立十九周年而写的。其中讲到，工人阶级派出宣传队，直接进入学校，进入上层建筑的各个领域，领导那里的斗、批、改，“这是无产阶级革命史上的伟大创举，是对马克思列宁主义的新发展”。毛泽东审阅时，删去了其中的“是对马克思列宁主义的新发展”。这篇社论在1968年10月1日《人民日报》《解放军报》和10月14日出版的《红旗》杂志第四期上发表。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"9930bfac15"}],"page":{"id":"0b11d642fb","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"9930bfac15","start":316,"end":316}}}},"__N_SSG":true}